{"tid":165593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國贏日本！ 成南韓民眾最討厭國家","createTime":"2017-03-21T12:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T13:13:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ff0ef4e08cfeefd45f6e48dcc459112e57a86c","tid":165593,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國因「薩德」議題掀起反韓動作，但也引發南韓方面不滿，兩國關係交惡，根據南韓當地調查，中國取代了日本，成為南韓民眾最討厭的國家。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/mar/21/images/bigPic/400_400/phpB8FEyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fmar%2F21%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpB8FEyk.jpg&h=c51de728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">南韓、中國因薩德議題交惡，圖為運送到南韓的薩德組件。（法新社）</span><br />\n《法新社》報導，南韓峨山政策研究院（Asan Institute for Policy Studies ）在6日到8日針對1000名南韓成年人進行調查，發現中國的分數從1月的4.31分，降到了3月的3.21分。該項調查以0分到10分做區分，10分為最喜歡。<br />\n因為日前「慰安婦」的外交爭端，日本的分數也從3.56分下降到3.33分。<br />\n峨山政策研究院對中國分數的大幅下滑感到驚訝，指出南韓民眾一直都很不喜歡日本，但這次調查顯示，比起日本（3.33分），南韓民眾更不喜歡中國（3.21分）。<br />\n調查也顯示，越來越多南韓民眾支持薩德，支持的比率從11月的46.3%，升至本次調查的50.6%，反對的比率則從45.7%下降到37.9%。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2011698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2011698&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6af5e0f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2011698&h=feae90c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2011698</a>"},{"pid":"54c559a67919156503e7cb4ec321a675e794176a","tid":165593,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"支那玩完啦"},{"pid":"3646b00e2c01dc20d13e6933d239f31f4fa14266","tid":165593,"uid":7704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"我比較想知咩國家人會鍾意中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}